# __PACKAGE_NAME__

Native Lynx library.

## Development

```bash
npm install
npm run codegen
```

The generated JS specs are written to `generated/`. Platform native module
typings live in `types/platform-native-module.d.ts`; NAPI native module typings
live in `types/napi-native-module.d.ts`. NAPI native modules use a minimal
shared C++ N-API callback stub. Selected native files are written to
__PLATFORM_DIRECTORY_LIST__. The package is discovered by Lynx through
`lynx.lib.json`.
